          <Pad Id="VjefoJii7tMQV0mf5vCamF" Bounds="518,539,249,180" ShowValueBox="true" isIOBox="true" Value="Quality vs Performance Trade-off&#xD;&#xA;• Low Step Size (many points):&#xD;&#xA;  - Higher quality, smoother curves&#xD;&#xA;  - Slower scanner movement capability&#xD;&#xA;  - Lower achievable frame rates&#xD;&#xA;• High Step Size (fewer points):&#xD;&#xA;  - Visible line segments on curves&#xD;&#xA;  - Faster scanner movement&#xD;&#xA;  - Higher achievable frame rates">
